{"type":"message","id":"bda027f1","parentId":"f91add64","timestamp":"2026-03-20T23:02:59.267Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The calendar and task APIs need user authorization. Let me check if there's a way to get this information or if I should just return a message about authorization needed. Let me try a different approach - maybe try to check if there's a refresh token or if the OAuth is already set up.\n\nActually, looking at the runtime info, it says `channel=feishu` with `capabilities=none`. This might mean the Feishu channel doesn't have full API capabilities enabled. Let me try to check the calendar anyway with the primary calendar action, and also check the tasklist.\n\nActually the error \"need_user_authorization\" suggests the OAuth user token is missing or expired. \n\nSince I can't retrieve the calendar and tasks without proper authorization, I'll need to send a message to the user explaining that this feature requires them to authorize access first.","thinkingSignature":"b0f8dc4882df8c9272bed5fca072bbcb4f2cb2b93a7ebef4f7bfa53a8d027b79"},{"type":"text","text":"今日行程概览（2026年3月21日 · 周六）：\n\n**⚠️ 暂无日程 & 待办**\n\n原因：飞书日历和任务接口需要用户授权才能读取数据。当前 OAuth 授权已过期或缺失。\n\n---\n**需要您操作：**\n请在 OpenClaw 配置中重新完成飞书用户授权，或联系管理员检查 `feishu_oauth` 相关配置。授权完成后我即可自动拉取您的日历和任务。\n\n如需立即恢复，可发送「授权」或「/feishu_doctor」触发诊断流程。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":932,"output":291,"cacheRead":36738,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":37961,"cost":{"input":0.0003728,"output":0.0004365,"cacheRead":0.00146952,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00227882}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774047767182}}
